Package: dimvR
Type: Package
Title: Conditional Distribution-Based Imputation of Missing Values with Regularization
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Yudha H", "Tejaningrat",
                  email = "yht.dev@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Yudha H Tejaningrat [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yudha H Tejaningrat <yht.dev@gmail.com>
Description: Implements conditional distribution-based imputation methods for
    missing values with regularization techniques. Supports deterministic and
    multiple imputation with Gaussian residual noise for Rubin-style variance
    pooling. Also includes experimental benchmarking, explainability, and
    reporting helpers for regression-focused workflows.
